VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'outputs that we got with this generation. all look basically the same. But here is the same prompt with the Pro model. And you\'ll notice that it\'s just about better in every single way. It still keeps the same warmth and all of that, but we have much more detail and'

[02:18] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'realism in every aspect of the image. Here\'s another example of the previous Nano Banana model. A bored teenager doodling in a notebook while glancing at the teacher struggling to stay awake as the afternoon sun streams through the windows. Here\'s a few examples of the'

