VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'we hear birds and other nature sounds in the background. The man says, "Are you ready to go?" And the woman says, "Almost. I just want to finish the cocoa and then we can go." Okay. And then he replies, "Okay." And puts his arm around her. That\'s the extent of the prompt.'

[09:04] [scene:talk]
