VISUAL:
AUDIO: '&gt;&gt; Are you ready to go? Almost. &gt;&gt; I just want to finish this cocoa and then we can go. Okay. &gt;&gt; Okay. Out of sage, right? Same exact problem. Looked great all the way up till the end and then we got this'

