AUDIO: 'gibberish at the end. We have a nice little butterfly flying in. Now, let\'s look at the Po 2 model. Are you ready to go? &gt;&gt; Almost. I just want to finish this Coco and then we can go. Okay.'

[09:56] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: '&gt;&gt; Okay. &gt;&gt; No extra words. We had birds chirping in the background. I believe it was the only one that put birds chirping in the background. Armarounder at the end. Everybody said their lines. No problems'

[10:09] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'whatsoever. It was absolutely perfect. And by the way, that model gave us a full 10 seconds. Whereas Veo 3.1 and Veo both just gave us eight. They also have a very strong AI avatar solution which allows you to take a still image of a'

[10:22] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'person, any person, and add audio on top of it to give you realistic motion of a talking avatar. Like here\'s an example. Now, this is an image that I actually created here in the platform combining an image of me and my soda can. And then I said he is enthusiastic about the soda'

